The paper deals with game theory, specifically the concept of equilibrium, and also introduces a novel interpretation of games in terms of Minkowski spacetime. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). The paper also involves information theory (cs.IT), social and information networks (cs.SI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and machine learning (cs.LG) in its mathematical framework and analysis.
